PN,36701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FVictims of a notorious grooming gang
OL,7,Fring leader have been told he cannot
OL,8,Fbe deported back to Pakistan when he
OL,9,Fis released in just days.
OL,11,FShabir Ahmed, 73, known to his victims
OL,12,Fas "Daddy", had dual British-Pakistan
OL,13,Fcitizenship and was stripped of his
OL,14,FBritish citizenship following his
OL,15,Fconviction in 2012 for multiple counts
OL,16,Fof rape and sexual offences against
OL,17,Fgirls in Rochdale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FBut documents published online -
OL,7,Fallegedly from the Probation Service
OL,8,Fto one of his victims - state he will
OL,9,Fbe released on 2 July and cannot be
OL,10,Fdeported back to Pakistan.
OL,12,FThis is due to provisions in the
OL,13,FImmigration Act 1971 which bar his
OL,14,Fremoval because he arrived in the UK
OL,15,Fbefore 1973 and has lived in the UK
OL,16,Ffor at least five years before his
OL,17,Fdeportation was considered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FIt is understood Ahmed will be
OL,7,Freleased on licence, that he must
OL,8,Finitially live at an accommodation
OL,9,Fwhich is staffed 24 hours and is
OL,10,Fsubject to an "exclusion zone" centred
OL,11,Fon Rochdale.
OL,13,FPaul Waugh, MP for Rochdale, told The
OL,14,FDaily Telegraph: "The people of
OL,15,FRochdale want him booted out of the
OL,16,Fcountry and it's simply unacceptable
OL,17,Fthat the government of Pakistan are
OL,18,Frefusing to take him back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,F"If the Citizenship Act needs to be
OL,7,Famended to do that, ministers should
OL,8,Flook at doing just that."
OL,10,FFor two years from early 2008, girls
OL,11,Fas young as 12 were plied with alcohol
OL,12,Fand drugs, gang-raped in rooms above
OL,13,Ftakeaway shops and ferried to
OL,14,Fdifferent flats in taxis where cash
OL,15,Fwas paid to use the girls for sex.
OL,17,FAt his trial, Ahmed called the judge
OL,18,Fracist and took his case to the
OL,19,FEuropean Court of Human Rights,
OL,20,Fclaiming he did not get a fair trial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FHe was jailed for 19 years in 2012 at
OL,7,FLiverpool Crown Court, as one of nine
OL,8,Fmen in the Rochdale grooming gang
OL,9,Ftrial convicted of offences against
OL,10,Ffive girls.
OL,12,FPolice said the victims were from
OL,13,F"chaotic", "council estate"
OL,14,Fbackgrounds and as many as 50 girls
OL,15,Fcould have been victims of the gang.
OL,17,FJudge Gerald Clifton said victims were
OL,18,Ftreated "as though they were worthless
OL,19,Fand beyond any respect" because they
OL,20,Fwere not part of the gang's community
OL,21,For religion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FIn 2022, Andy Burnham, who is likely
OL,7,Fto replace Sir Keir Starmer as the
OL,8,Fnext prime minister, called on the
OL,9,FConservative government "to do
OL,10,Feverything within... the government's
OL,11,Fpower" to deport grooming gang members.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police said at the
OL,14,Ftime there was no "racial or cultural"
OL,15,Felement to the crimes.
OL,17,FA report later found that police did
OL,18,Fnot act despite multiple concerns
OL,19,Fbeing raised, citing "serious multiple
OL,20,Ffailures" by police and local
OL,21,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FAhmed's case follows a similar legal
OL,7,Fbattle by two other gang members, Qari
OL,8,FAbdul Rauf and Adil Khan.
OL,10,FBoth were stripped of their British
OL,11,Fcitizenship in 2022, 10 years after
OL,12,Ftheir convictions, after fighting a
OL,13,Flong legal battle which went all the
OL,14,Fway to the Court of Appeal.
OL,16,FQari Abdul Rauf and Adil Khan invoked
OL,17,Ftheir human rights under article eight
OL,18,Fof the European Convention on Human
OL,19,FRights, the right to a private and
OL,20,Ffamily life, to avoid deportation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,FThe Home Office has not said if either
OL,7,Fhave been deported.
OL,9,FA spokeswoman for the Home Office
OL,10,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are first and
OL,11,Fforemost with the victims of these
OL,12,Fappalling crimes.
OL,14,F"Ahmed's horrific crimes were at the
OL,15,Fheart of the grooming gangs scandal
OL,16,Fthat represents one of the darkest
OL,17,Fmoments in our country's history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,F"The most vulnerable people were
OL,7,Fabused and exploited at the hands of
OL,8,Fevil child rapists, and must face the
OL,9,Ffull force of the law.
OL,11,F"On his release he will be on the sex
OL,12,Foffenders' register for life, ordered
OL,13,Fto stay away from his victims and
OL,14,Fbanned from contacting any child or
OL,15,Fyoung person.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782884874
OL,3,CGrooming gang 'Daddy' set for release
OL,4,Cand 'cannot be deported'
OL,6,F"As well as facing strict curfews and
OL,7,Frestriction zones, his every movement
OL,8,Fwill be tracked, forced to wear an
OL,9,Felectronic tag. Should he breach his
OL,10,Fconditions, he will be immediately
OL,11,Flocked up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
